<P>
On Feb. 11, a small bright spot appeared in the dark, gaping abyss called 
"White South Africa." A time to rejoice, yes, but it is also a time for a new 
beginning for the 23 million freedom fighters to attain what every living 
person should have: a right to stand up and be counted, to speak and resist 
