ENVIRONMENT; ENVIRONMENTAL IMPACT STATEMENTS; LOCAL GOVERNMENT; ORDINANCES; 
CALIFORNIA -- SUITS; CALIFORNIA -- AGRICULTURE; NATURAL RESOURCES DEFENSE 
COUNCIL 
</P>
