AGRICULTURE; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- SUITS; ORANGE COUNTY -- SUITS; HEALTH 
HAZARDS; DEUKMEJIAN, GEORGE; PUBLIC HEALTH 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
