<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY NEWSMAKERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
* James R. Morrell has joined American Suzuki Motor Corp.'s automotive division 
in Brea as Los Angeles regional sales manager. 
</P>
<P>
He is responsible for overseeing all sales operations, advertising and dealer 
development activities in the 14-state region. Morrell had previously been Los 
Angeles regional manager for Peugeot Motors of America from 1986 through 1989. 
Earlier positions include national sales manager and regional manager for Isuzu 
Truck of America in Los Angeles and Western regional manager for American Isuzu 
Motors. 
</P>
